's Award===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Time # !! Year !! PD's Award\n|-\n| 1st || 2001 || none\n|-\n| 2nd || 2002 || none\n|-\n| 3rd || 2003 || [[Kim Hyun-chul (comedian)|Kim Hyun-chul]]<br>[[MC Mong]]<br>[[Joo Young-hoon]]\n|-\n| 4th || 2004 || [[MC Mong]]<br>[[Jo Hye-ryun]]<br>[[Park Soo-hong]]<br>[[Yoon Jung-soo]]\n|-\n| 5th || 2005 || [[Kim Yong-man (comedian)|Kim Yong-man]]<br>[[Jo Hye-ryun]]\n|-\n| 6th || 2006 || [[:ko:\uc870\ud615\uae30|Jo Hyung-ki]]\n|-\n| 7th || 2007 || [[Lee Kyung-kyu]]<br>[[Kim Yong-man (comedian)|Kim Yong-man]]\n|-\n| 8th || 2008 || [[Infinite Challenge]]\n|-\n| 9th || 2009 || [[Yoo Jae-suk]]\n|-\n| 10th || 2010 || none\n|-\n| 11th || 2011 || [[Yoon Jong-shin]]<br>[[Kim Won-hee]]\n|-\n| 12th || 2012 || [[Yoo Jae-suk]]\n|-\n| 13th || 2013 || [[Kim Sung-joo (presenter)|Kim Sung-joo]]<br>[[Seo Kyung-seok]]\n|-\n| 14th || 2014 || [[Haha (entertainer)|Haha]]<br>[[Jung Woong-in]]\n|-\n| 15th || 2015 || [[Golden Fishery|Radio Star]]\n|-\n| 16th || 2016 || [[Kim Gu-ra]]\n|-\n| 17th || 2017 || ''[[King of Mask Singer]]'' team\n|-\n| 18th || 2018 || ''[[Real Man 300]]'' team\n|}\n\n===Screenwriter of the Year Award===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Time # !! Year !! Variety !! Radio\n|-\n| 1st || 2016 || Lee Ae-young<br/>''[[Real Men (TV series)|Real Men]]'' || Park Geum-sun<br/>''Women's Time''\n|-\n| 2nd || 2017 || Lee Kyung-ha<br/>''[[I Live Alone (TV series)|I Live Alone]]'' || Lee Yoon-yong<br/>''Two O'clock Hurray!''\n|-\n| 3rd || 2018 || Yeo Hyun-jeon<br/>''[[Omniscient Interfering View]]'' || {{N/A}}\n|-\n| 4th || 2019 || Jung Da-won<br/>''{{illm|Where Is My Home|ko|\uad6c\ud574\uc918! \ud648\uc988}}'' || {{N/A}}\n|}\n\n===Best Entertainer Award===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Time # !! Year !! Variety !! Music/Talk !! Sitcom\n|-\n| 1st || 2018 || [[Sung Hoon]]<br/>[[Yoo Byung-jae]] || [[Lee Sang-min (singer)|Lee Sang-min]